\end_layout

\end_inset


\begin_inset Argument 4
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout
Tools to assess the dissimilarity between multivariate time series by using
 the psi measure described in "Numerical methods in Quaternary pollen analysis"
 (Birks and Gordon, 1985).
 The algorithm computes a matrix of distances (euclidean, manhattan, chi)
 between all sample pairs, and minimizes the sum of distances, constrained
 by sample order.
\end_layout

\end_inset


