literal "false"

\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\end_inset


\begin_inset Argument 4
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout
Mechanistical model simulating the range shift of 
\shape italic
Quercus pyrenaica 
\shape default
in the Sierra Nevada National Park (Granada, Spain) under different climate
 warming scenarios.
 Range shift is modeled as an emergent property of the acorn-dispersal behavior
 of the Eurasian Jay, the changing climatic conditions in the tree line,
 and the topographic structure of the terrain.
\end_layout

\end_inset


